<p>Hello <b><%= @resource.username %></b>!</p>

<p>Looks like you forgot your password, huh! No problem, though.</p>

<p><%= link_to 'Change your password', 
  edit_password_url(@resource, :reset_password_token => @resource.reset_password_token) %></p>

<p>If you didn't request this, please ignore this email.</p>
<p>Your password won't change until you access the link above and create a new one.</p>
